-- AbitibiBowater Seeking Acquisitions to Help Reduce Reliance on Newsprint
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   D o n v i l l e
-- 2010-12-10T19:33:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-10/abitibibowater-seeking-acquisitions-to-help-reduce-reliance-on-newsprint.html
AbitibiBowater Inc., a Canadian
newsprint maker, is considering acquisitions to help the company
reduce its reliance on the product as North American demand
drops, Chairman Dick Evans said today in a telephone interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christopher Donville in Vancouver at 
